Package: fundfi
Type: Package
Title: Fundamental XBRL financial analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christopher Wilson
Maintainer: Christopher Wilson <christopher@figaredo.net>
Description: This package acts as a wrapper for the edgarWebR
    and XBRL packages, making it easy to download any XBRL document
    from the SEC EDGAR's service using tickers. It also formats 
    the balance sheet, income statement and cash flow. Finally 
    it does percentage analysis, finantial indicators, 
    variance and merging statements.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.1)
Imports:
    edgarWebR,
    XBRL,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    stringr
Suggests:
    knitr,
    devtools,
    roxygen2,
    testthat,
    pander
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
